@NODE "Usage" "Usage"
@TOC "Main"

@{FG SHINE}____________________________________________________________________________@{FG TEXT}
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
                                  U S A G E
@{FG SHINE}____________________________________________________________________________@{FG TEXT}
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
From Workbench:
 Double click on its icon and enter a username and a password, then click 
on "Go!" to lock out!

From CLI or Shell:
 Either type Passcode at the prompt or use the default arguments for the 
CLI which are:

        "Passcode [Username] [Password]

 Remember, Passcode requires you to enter the password and username with 
capital and lower case letters in all the right places!

   @{" Back to the Contents Page! " LINK "Main"}
